      • syncType

      • syncToken

      • dateFrom

        public java.lang.String dateFrom
        The start datetime for resulting records in (ISO 8601)[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601] format including timezone, for example 2016-03-10T18:07:52.534Z. The default value is the current moment Format: date-time

      • recordCount

        public java.lang.Long recordCount
        For 'FSync' the parameter is mandatory, it limits the number of records to be returned in response. For 'ISync' it specifies with how many records to extend sync Frame to the past, the maximum number of records is 250

      • statusGroup

        public java.lang.String[] statusGroup
        Type of calls to be returned. The default value is 'All' Enum: Missed, All

      • view

        public java.lang.String view
        View of call records. The same view parameter specified for FSync will be applied for ISync, the view cannot be changed for ISync Default: Simple Enum: Simple, Detailed

      • showDeleted

        public java.lang.Boolean showDeleted
        Supported for ISync. If 'True' then deleted call records are returned
